    <h2>Wascomat — Electrolux Professional, Sweden, Laundrylux</h2>
    <p>Wascomat is the US-market commercial laundry brand within the Electrolux Professional family. The chassis engineering originates from Electrolux Professional Laundry in Sweden (Ljungby manufacturing), distributed and serviced in the US under the Wascomat badge through Laundrylux as the long-time US authorized distributor. This distribution arrangement gives Wascomat a distinctive LA footprint: loyal to specific operator segments, European engineering heritage in the control platform and cycle programming, and parts-supply routed through the Electrolux Professional + Laundrylux channel rather than through Alliance (Speed Queen/UniMac/Huebsch) or Dexter distribution.</p>
    <p>The practical LA laundromat operator takeaway: if your spec is Wascomat, your parts channel is Electrolux Professional + Laundrylux — common service parts (door gaskets, door switches, drain pumps, water-inlet valves, drive belts) carry 1-3 day lead time through the authorized distributor, and specialty parts for Crossover 2.0 VFD drives or EnvoyUltra control boards run 3-7 days. We stock common Wascomat service parts on the truck for single-visit resolution where model compatibility matches.</p>
